0:00:00.100 --> 0:00:04.560 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
Ramayana is the cultural backbone of the country.

0:00:04.880 --> 0:00:08.240 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
But let us not consider the story of Ramayana as just history.

0:00:11.230 --> 0:00:13.720 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
It has spirituality in it.

0:00:14.330 --> 0:00:16.230 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
And it starts from Navratri.

0:00:16.870 --> 0:00:20.810 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
For nine days, there was a fierce battle between Ram and Ravan. 

0:00:21.350 --> 0:00:24.130 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
And on the tenth day, Ravan dies.

0:00:24.670 --> 0:00:25.970 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
Which is called Dussehra.

0:00:25.970 --> 0:00:32.930 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
