0:00:34.830 --> 0:00:35.510 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
Squirrels.

0:00:35.790 --> 0:00:37.590 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
And in front of them were demons.

0:00:38.210 --> 0:00:39.550 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
It signifies something.

0:00:39.810 --> 0:00:41.510 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
What is your mind like?

0:00:42.320 --> 0:00:42.700 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
Like a monkey.

0:00:46.260 --> 0:00:48.160 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
And on the other side, what is your mind like?

0:00:48.360 --> 0:00:49.040 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
Like a demon.

0:00:49.580 --> 0:00:50.200 line:13 position:50% align:center size:80%
